channel.title: Hybrid pvp v3 Cache
channel.description:
right i realy dont know how to put this but its made me realy upset.
I spent so much time on a hybrid pvp server yeah and the client was working perfectly.
Some people started complaining saying the cache would not download for them so I thought , Right . Il try it on a different laptop ,
So i went on my mums laptop and went and downloaded my client and they was right. the client would not download the cache , I tried the cache download link and it was down so i knew this was the problem.
The thing is i dont know how to make it work again , Would anyone help me by teamviewing me or something and fixing it? It would help me alot and i will pay for this simple fix?
If you could please Reply or Pm me?
